The paper deals with regression under the "extremely small n large p" condition, which is a common problem in machine learning and statistics. The focus is on incorporating expert knowledge to improve prediction accuracy. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computational engineering, finance, and science (cs.CE), cryptography and security (cs.CR), and databases (cs.DB).
